  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Gateway JSON / Complex Txns",
      "description": "15 complex transactions. These requests will produce database activity, and many of them also trigger internal HTTP sub-calls to /waimai/internal/*.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "PLACE_ORDER",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"txnCode\": \"PLACE_ORDER\",\n  \"params\": {\n    \"customerId\": \"{{customerId}}\",\n    \"merchantId\": \"{{merchantId}}\",\n    \"orderId\": \"{{orderId}}\",\n    \"productId\": \"{{productId}}\",\n    \"productName\": \"{{productName}}\",\n    \"basePrice\": \"{{basePrice}}\",\n    \"originalAmount\": \"{{originalAmount}}\",\n    \"amount\": \"{{amount}}\",\n    \"keyword\": \"{{keyword}}\",\n    \"quantity\": \"{{quantity}}\",\n    \"rating\": \"{{rating}}\",\n    \"riderId\": \"{{riderId}}\",\n    \"complaintId\": \"{{complaintId}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/waimai/gateway/json",
            "description": "交易码字段：txnCode\n子调用：POST /waimai/internal/pricing, POST /waimai/internal/discount, POST /waimai/internal/risk\n数据库：INSERT orders\n特点：最适合做录制回放样本，既有 DB 写入，也有 3 个 HTTP 子调用"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "CONFIRM_ORDER",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
